  <title>Manual Operation</title>
  <body>
    <header>
      <para styleclass="Heading4">Manual Operation</para>
    </header>
    <para styleclass="Normal">Manual operation of the drum conveyor can be performed with the following methods.</para>
    <para styleclass="Normal"></para>
    <para styleclass="Normal"><text style="font-weight:bold;">A    Procedure to Rotate in Forward Direction During Automatic Operation</text></para>
    <para styleclass="Normal"></para>
    <list id="2" type="ol" listtype="decimal" formatstring="%0:s)" format-charset="DEFAULT_CHARSET" levelreset="true" legalstyle="false" startfrom="1" styleclass="1_11mm" style="margin-top:0px; margin-bottom:8px; font-family:Arial; font-size:11pt; color:#000000;">
      <li styleclass="1_11mm" style="margin-top:0px; margin-bottom:8px;"><text styleclass style="font-family:Arial; font-size:11pt; color:#000000;">Press the “Manual Intervention” switch. (Manual operation mode)</text></li>
      <li styleclass="1_11mm" style="margin-top:0px; margin-bottom:8px;"><text styleclass style="font-family:Arial; font-size:11pt; color:#000000;">Press the “Forward Rotation Start” switch (starts rotation in forward direction).</text></li>
      <li styleclass="1_11mm" style="margin-top:0px; margin-bottom:8px;"><text styleclass style="font-family:Arial; font-size:11pt; color:#000000;">Press the “Forward Rotation Start” switch again (stops rotation in forward direction).</text></li>
      <li styleclass="1_11mm" style="margin-top:0px; margin-bottom:8px;"><text styleclass style="font-family:Arial; font-size:11pt; color:#000000;">Press the “Manual Intervention” switch. (Automatic operation mode)</text></li>
    </list>
    <para styleclass="Normal"></para>
    <para styleclass="Normal"><text style="font-weight:bold;">B    Procedure to Rotate in Reverse Direction During Automatic Operation</text></para>
    <para styleclass="Normal"></para>
    <list id="3" type="ol" listtype="decimal" formatstring="%0:s)" format-charset="DEFAULT_CHARSET" levelreset="true" legalstyle="false" startfrom="1" styleclass="1_11mm" style="margin-top:0px; margin-bottom:8px; font-family:Arial; font-size:11pt; color:#000000;">
      <li styleclass="1_11mm" style="margin-top:0px; margin-bottom:8px;"><text styleclass style="font-family:Arial; font-size:11pt; color:#000000;">Press the “Manual Intervention” switch. (Manual operation mode).</text></li>
      <li styleclass="1_11mm" style="margin-top:0px; margin-bottom:8px;"><text styleclass style="font-family:Arial; font-size:11pt; color:#000000;">Hold down the “Reverse Rotation Start” switch (rotation in reverse direction).</text></li>
      <li styleclass="1_11mm" style="margin-top:0px; margin-bottom:8px;"><text styleclass style="font-family:Arial; font-size:11pt; color:#000000;">Release the “Reverse Rotation Start” switch (stops rotation in reverse direction).</text></li>
      <li styleclass="1_11mm" style="margin-top:0px; margin-bottom:8px;"><text styleclass style="font-family:Arial; font-size:11pt; color:#000000;">Press the “Manual Intervention” switch. (Automatic operation mode)</text></li>
    </list>
    <para styleclass="1_11mm" style="margin-top:0px; margin-bottom:8px; margin-left:22px;"></para>
    <para styleclass="1_11mm" style="margin-top:0px; margin-bottom:8px; margin-left:22px;">-NOTE-</para>
    <para styleclass="1_11mm" style="margin-top:0px; margin-left:22px;"><text style="font-size:10pt;">The switches are located on the drum conveyor operation panel (hereafter called operation panel).</text></para>
    <para styleclass="1_11mm" style="margin-top:0px; margin-bottom:8px; margin-left:22px;"><text style="font-size:10pt;">(Refer to </text><link displaytype="text" defaultstyle="false" type="topiclink" href="15_2-Drum-Conveyor-(Option)" anchor="Fig15.3" style="font-size:10pt; color:#0000ff;">Figure 15.3</link><text style="font-size:10pt;">)</text></para>
  </body>
